apps.localizedDescription:
Credits: KEEP THE CREDITS IF YOU WANT TO RE-UP MY IPA! 
- Alfhaily for Cercube.
- Galactic-Dev for the original iSponsorBlock, @Luewii for his fork of iSponsorBlock (which works in jailed mode).
- PoomSmart for YTUHD and YTClassicVideoQuality.
- Julioverne for removing Cercube ads.
- CrazyMind90 for YTDisableUglySuggestions.
- Al4ise for Azule - a tool used to inject jailbreak tweaks into jailed iOS apps! 
- Huge thanks to u/el_zari, the best tester I ever worked with. Plus many, many other testers. 

 Features:
 CercubeNoAds: make sure you log in to Cercube first.
- SponsorBlock: skip sponsor ads inside video.
- YTUHD: unlock 1440 & 2140p quality.
- YTClassicVideoQuality: brings back the original video quality selector.
- YTDisableUglySuggestions: remove suggested videos that show up as thumbnails at the end of some Youtube videos. 

 Known issues:
- Does not work on iOS 12 and below because iSponsorBlock requires iOS 13+.
- iSponsorBlock: on YouTube v16.22.5, modified time doesn't show up in the videos progress bar.
- YTUHD may not work. Watching high-quality video (1440p+) may causing battery drain/laggy/hot.
- Install the iPA using Filza won't work. Not sure why you need the iPA if you're jailbroken, though...
